             was indicted for <rs id="t18010415-43-off230" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010415-43-off230" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010415-43-off230" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010415-43-cd231" type="crimeDate">20th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010415-43-off230 t18010415-43-cd231"></join>, a tray, value 6d. and twenty-seven gold rings, value 5l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010415-43-victim417" type="victimName">
                     Gabriel 
                     Aughtie
                  <interp inst="t18010415-43-victim417" type="surname" value="Aughtie"></interp>
